web fuzzing:
ffuf -u http://10.10.21.202/FUZZ -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/big.txt
ffuf -u http://10.10.21.202/FUZZ -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-medium-words-lowercase.txt -e .txt
ffuf -u http://10.10.21.202/indexFUZZ -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/web-extensions.txt
ffuf -u http://10.10.21.202/FUZZ -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-medium-files-lowercase.txt
ffuf -u http://10.10.21.202/FUZZ -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-medium-directories-lowercase.txt -t 100

wfuzz -u admin.holo.live/FUZZ.php -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/big.txt
wfuzz -u http://admin.holo.live/FUZZ.php -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/big.txt --hc 404 -v -t 50
wfuzz -c -L --hc=404 -w WORDLIST TARGET **L=recursivo**
wfuzz -c --hc=404 -w WORDLIST -w WORDLIST2 url/FUZZ/FUZ2Z

filtros:
ffuf -u http://10.10.21.202/FUZZ -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-medium-files-lowercase.txt -t 100 -fc 403 fc=filter code
ffuf -u http://10.10.21.202/FUZZ -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-medium-files-lowercase.txt -t 100 -mc 200 mc=match code
ffuf -u http://10.10.21.202/FUZZ -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-medium-files-lowercase.txt -fr '/\..*' -t 100 fr=filter regexp
ffuf -u http://10.10.235.197/FUZZ -c -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/directory-list-2.3-medium.txt -ic ic=ignore comments en wordlists

fuzzing parametros:
ffuf -u 'http://10.10.235.197/sqli-labs/Less-1/?FUZZ=1' -c -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/burp-parameter-names.txt fw=filter words
ffuf -u 'http://MACHINE_IP/sqli-labs/Less-1/?FUZZ=1' -c -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-medium-words-lowercase.txt 

for i in {0..255}; do echo $i; done | ffuf -u 'http://MACHINE_IP/sqli-labs/Less-1/?id=FUZZ' -c -w - -fw 33 //-w -=lee desde stdout en este caso una lista de numeros del 0 al 255
seq 0 255 | ffuf -u 'http://MACHINE_IP/sqli-labs/Less-1/?id=FUZZ' -c -w - -fw 33

subdomain fuzzing:
ffuf -u http://FUZZ.google.com -c -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt -fs 0
ffuf -u http://google.com -c -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt -H 'Host: FUZZ.google.com' -fs 0
gobuster vhost -u http://holo.live -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-110000.txt -t 100 -o vhosts.log
wfuzz -u <URL> -w <wordlist> -H "Host: FUZZ.example.com" --hc <status codes to hide>

enviando trafico ffuf a un proxy:
ffuf -u http://10.10.235.197/ -c -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/common.txt -x http://127.0.0.1:8080

